---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Explainable AI Fraud Intelligence" description="The transparent, lending-native fraud shield that explains itself and stops tomorrow's threats today.">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_80%_50%_at_50%_-20%,rgba(251,191,36,0.15),transparent)]" />
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-normal tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        The transparent fraud shield that <span class="text-amber-400">explains itself</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-xl text-slate-400">
        Clarifid is a Glass Box AI module for lending. Every decision comes with a traceable, audit-ready report. Built for mortgage, tenant screening, and loan validation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="rounded-md bg-amber-500 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-950 hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors">
          Partner with us
        </a>
        <a href="/product" class="rounded-md border border-slate-600 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 hover:border-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
          See how it works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-normal text-white md:text-4xl">The problem with black-box AI</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-400">
        Existing fraud platforms return risk scores without explaining why. Users can't debug blocked transactions, prove compliance, or tune rules. ~35% false positives decline legitimate borrowers. 2026 threats—deepfakes, synthetic identities—outpace pre-AI platforms.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-amber-400">Black-box scores</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">No explanations. Can't debug, prove, or tune.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-amber-400">~35% false positives</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Legitimate borrowers declined. Conversions lost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-amber-400">2026 threat blindness</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Deepfakes, synthetic IDs outpacing legacy systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-normal text-white md:text-4xl">The Glass Box difference</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-400">
        Clarifid plugs into partner platforms as a sidecar module. Every decision includes traceable reason codes and natural-language explanations.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Glass Box Logic</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">SHAP/LIME-based explainability. Traceable decision trees for every flag.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Synthetic ID Shield</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Graph neural networks detecting identity linkage patterns across applications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Deepfake Defense</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Hardware-anchored biometric verification using device secure enclaves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Lending-Native Rules</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Purpose-built for mortgage, tenant screening, loan validation—not e-commerce.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Privacy-First Design</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">PII hashed before logging. Data residency for PIPEDA/CCPA/GDPR.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white">Sub-100ms latency</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Edge-native on Cloudflare Workers. 300+ global locations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-normal text-white md:text-4xl">Built for technology partners</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-400">
        We operate as an OEM/white-label supplier. Sell to Socure, Sift, SEON, Jumio, Signifyd as the missing module they embed or resell.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-8 text-slate-500">
        <span>Socure RiskOS</span>
        <span>Sift</span>
        <span>SEON</span>
        <span>Jumio</span>
        <span>Signifyd</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-amber-500 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-950 hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors">
          Start a partnership
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
